data.description: Buyers Lookout! This 2021 Richmond American Home build is in the coveted Trailmark community.  This 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom residence is a modern oasis boasting stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and laminate floors in the kitchen and lower living area. Upstairs, you'll find an expansive living space, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The master bathroom features a spacious standing shower, offering a touch of luxury. Outside, a paver driveway leads to a spacious 3-car garage, ensuring ample parking and storage.  The community offers a host of amenities, including a community pool, tennis courts, basketball court, volleyball courts, walking trails, and more. This property combines comfort and convenience with a vibrant community atmosphere.  Don't miss out on seeing this beautiful home for yourself.
